### Disable direct access
Host bitbucket.org
  HostName DO_NOT_ACCESS_BITBUCKET_DIRECTLY!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!

Host github.com
  HostName DO_NOT_ACCESS_GITHUB_DIRECTLY!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!

Host gitlab.com
  HostName DO_NOT_ACCESS_GITLAB_DIRECTLY!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!

### Restrict access only by Identity file + default settings
Host bitbucket.org-*
  IdentitiesOnly yes
  HostName bitbucket.org
  StrictHostKeyChecking no
  User git

Host github.com-*
  IdentitiesOnly yes
  HostName github.com
  StrictHostKeyChecking no
  User git

Host gitlab.com-*
  IdentitiesOnly yes
  HostName gitlab.com
  StrictHostKeyChecking no
  User git
